zeus.actors
Class PlanRecord

java.lang.Object
  zeus.actors.PlanRecord
All Implemented Interfaces:
SuppliedRequester
public class PlanRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements SuppliedRequester

PlanRecord is used to manage the execution of a (primitive, mutable or infered) task. The field task is the primitive task being executed, the field thread is the ZeusTask that is actually being run
